Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.41,0:01:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是对比自己小五岁的女生说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.35,0:01:16.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽莎  我读了你的毕业论文
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:22.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  卡蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.99,0:01:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次和你见面会是在战场上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.75,0:01:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话我可不想和你为敌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.65,0:01:31.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马内金…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会在A-LAWS…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:41.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校  苏伊尔王国的动向如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:34.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还毫无变化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我觉得总有一天会改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反对中东重制计划的苏伊尔国力不能小觑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果苏伊尔做出行动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别的国家必定会纷纷跟从
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了阻止这种事态发生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:53.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦政府决定派遣独立治安维持部队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派A-LAWS？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦军已驻扎在苏伊尔的国境线了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此举可认为是对苏伊尔的牵制吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个国王的话  面对联邦是不会退让的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然拥有世界第一的信息产业
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但中东全境通讯处于如此封锁状态
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.12,0:04:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那信息也就无作作为了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于联邦的信息操作  中东的现状更不为世界所知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏伊尔军事能力如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然了解得不是很详细
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎拥有中东第一的军备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在联邦设立之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.44,0:04:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依靠稀有金属和信息产业成为中东第一富国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真鲁莽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样也绝不是联邦的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是苏伊尔  这4年中也开发不出性能超过联邦的新型兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算我们出手相助也是杯水车薪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把苏伊尔所持有的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即联邦对中东施行的恶政
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.41,0:05:02.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过我们卡塔隆的网络组织向全球发布
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舆论有了反对的呼声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦对中东也就不敢妄为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来  就有与苏伊尔进行交涉的必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池田  能与王室联系上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托当记者时期的朋友应该…没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.54,0:05:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了中东…不  是为了世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.81,0:05:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳  阿扎提斯坦情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.62,0:05:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国民都怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:40.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从发表建立了临时政府后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就没有什么吸引眼球的报道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.77,0:05:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信息管制也完全依照联邦的意愿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想去看看阿扎提斯坦的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国境线也被联邦军封锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直束手无策
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:06:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要重建阿扎提斯坦只有打倒联邦一条路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要战斗啊  作为公主的你有这个义务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.79,0:06:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  战争只能引发更多的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:12.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为人民能在用武力夺回的阿扎提斯坦上安居乐业吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你想忍气吞声吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已是亡国奴了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.62,0:06:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席琳  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你什么也别做就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来战斗  不这样做就不能夺回祖国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:39.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  我现在能理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了故乡…克鲁吉斯的你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仿佛自己的安身之处渐渐消失似的…这种失落感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:54.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了这种心情  为何你还能战斗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:06:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据观察班的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:04.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being的宇宙船极有可能前往拉格朗日3
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于林特少校接到特殊任务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.39,0:07:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此追击Gundam的任务由你来完成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.23,0:07:12.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增援也准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待你能为杰江中校报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九条…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:29.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米里奥！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:33.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次事件成为了她心中永远的芥蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:39.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此便倒向宣扬以根除战争为理念的Celestial Being吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢至极
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.01,0:07:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事只是愚蠢的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:49.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纷争不可能从这世界上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.33,0:07:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不就是为了防止战事延长才当上战术预报员的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校  我给您拿饭来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别私自进来！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对布林格下达了攻击命令
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会怎么接招呢？Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:23.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各传感器  全部正常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子供给规定值确认
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎提斯坦被…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的国家…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿尔·萨谢斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我也一事无成…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E传感器有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有机影接近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人  是A-LAWS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:58.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了  某种危险的…东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种危险的…东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近的机体速度达到了78千秒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这么快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机居然只有一架？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios和Seravee还在修理中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam紧急出发  狙击敌机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO  先行出发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭载了伪太阳炉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.67,0:09:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是A-LAWS！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种机动性…又是新型机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:09:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦居然有能用Field的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能用TRANS-AM的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.37,0:10:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台新机型  居然压倒了OO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.22,0:10:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌机撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.17,0:10:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也太快了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收Gundam之后  以最快速度前往拉格朗日3
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  敌人这是出的哪一招？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要告诉我们他们的军队已经摆好了阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.66,0:10:51.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也向我们展示了新型机的性能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的牵制和警告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来更加需要O-Raizer了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是马内金的佯攻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没错  那架新型机的驾驶员是改革者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握了吠陀的他们能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:14.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能开发使用GN Field的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:16.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:19.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不说出他们的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…是犹豫了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林特少校  情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照预定顺利进行中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整理好情况就向我报告
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.22,0:11:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直接指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.85,0:11:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:48.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与统一政府作对的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们将遭遇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天降之雷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是神之审判
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=========================
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舱门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激光传感器与托勒密同步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.96,0:12:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密  降落
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3  2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰舷对接完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,固定用机械臂开始对接
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:42.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同步舱门对接完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你们很久了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜  过得还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:13:00.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才  好像在叫妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:06.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  你们是第一次见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳达·瓦斯提
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.26,0:13:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是犯罪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.73,0:13:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑就此打住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密和Gundam的补给和维修能不能快些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:21.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS的部队正在这片空域展开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:28.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为这里的伪装很完美的  明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是补给和整备最少也要5天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.69,0:13:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没见过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.98,0:13:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  我是重新开始活动的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被Celestial Being撬来的亚琉·利塔娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:42.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撬来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:43.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王留美介绍来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚琉很厉害的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:51.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅是宇宙物理学  MS工程学  还是再生治疗的权威
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会驾驶舰艇  做饭  外加还是个大美人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  相当优秀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:00.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,池田发来的加密电文
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏伊尔那边好像同意了会谈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.44,0:14:14.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  他们同意了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会谈就由我去吧  这里的指挥就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保险起见带上护卫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.51,0:14:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是红色的车子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.82,0:14:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.17,0:14:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏伊尔被坏人盯上了是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.36,0:14:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去打扰公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉  因为这孩子是来自苏伊尔的  一直非常的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么大家不能和平相处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.63,0:14:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以得想出个让大家和平相处的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.40,0:14:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起吃饭就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个点子很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:14:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它还有什么别的方法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩  一起唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.24,0:15:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有让大家互相看看自己宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是O-Raizer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这部机体有控制Twin-Drive系统的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有对TRANS-AM的增幅机能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.80,0:15:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的机体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios用的支援机 GN-Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN-Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.42,0:15:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始测试咯  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.80,0:15:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉格朗治3里居然有这种大规模的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.04,0:15:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道如何是好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.04,0:16:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我的错  很多人被夺去了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.37,0:16:07.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须为犯下的罪孽有所偿还
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:13.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是战斗  杀人这种事  我怎么也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到是很自然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不做点什么  力所能及的事也…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  能冒昧地问一句么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你接下来还准备和他在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.36,0:16:33.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  只要阿雷路亚还在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:36.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使会被卷进战争里也…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:41.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经是军人  也有了这种觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我已经决定了  不管发生什么也不和阿雷路亚分开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有个想要如此的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能够再会的话  一定再也不要分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  不知为什么很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.44,0:17:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的不安
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙空间以地面人员进行补充
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.27,0:17:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连新机体也
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.23,0:17:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新机体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也给我一台新机体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:29.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上校…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到连你也会加入A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是吹的什么风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.16,0:17:40.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子沉默寡言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会动用Memento mori
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Memento mori？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  利冯兹终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用Memento mori
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:57.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来中东计划就会加速  人类的意志将会统一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统一？要每个人之间都没有差别吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.45,0:18:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是统一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是将其集中成为我们原本的思想的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.01,0:18:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你协助Memento mori的建设
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待改革者所创建的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米海尔和约翰哥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把两个哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吗  我就觉得在什么地方见过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.95,0:18:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的那位小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得很有女人味了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟我打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:53.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会要了你好不容易捡回来的小命的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:08.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Raizer与OO对接完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部分对接  All Green
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.42,0:19:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  刹那  开始测试O-Raizer的控制系统
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.61,0:19:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:48.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扫射形态变形完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电力补给98%
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.64,0:19:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功率固定在6800
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标地点误差修正完成
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扫射功率没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准将  扫射准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  开始倒数
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始倒数
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离扫射还有  10
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按你说的去找了一下  但是没有找到符合的  大将
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.76,0:20:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么  那算了  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的委托人是大将  随你差遣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算不上是作为道歉吧  你也来看一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为你一定会很高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离TRANS-AM开始还有  8
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.56,0:20:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:41.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扫射开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.49,0:20:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.93,0:22:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离TRANS-AM开启还有  5
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.08,0:22:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.08,0:22:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.05,0:22:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.11,0:22:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.22,0:22:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM启动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.54,0:22:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓扑缺陷向高位转移
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.27,0:22:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子产生量  粒子放出量  一同上升
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.84,0:22:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超过了通常值的89%  继续上升
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.75,0:22:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要启动了  琳达
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.03,0:22:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.37,0:23:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,230
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.83,0:23:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,260
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.10,0:23:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.09,0:23:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破290%
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.87,0:23:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.73,0:23:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超过理论界限值
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.55,0:23:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.14,0:23:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是伊奥利亚预言的Twin-Drive
